data.description: Lovely home with spacious yard and covered front porch. This 3 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 garage home has been updated and is move-in ready! As soon as you walk in you will notice pride in ownership. All flooring in home has been recently replaced with solid surface, high quality luxury vinyl plank.  Walls have been freshly painted and baseboards replaced in many of the rooms.  Ceilings are finished with skip trowel texture; no popcorn finish!  Kitchen is spacious and has a newly installed banister.  Many light fixtures have been updated. Upstairs includes primary bedroom with spacious attached bathroom with large closet and 2 additional bedrooms along with an additional updated bathroom.  If you are looking for a separate workshop or dedicated private office, on the side of the home you will be delighted to find this desired space; complete with electrical outlets, lighting, and insulation.  The lower level of the home has a wood-burning fireplace and sliding doors which walk out to a concrete patio. The modified basement is a perfect area for additional storage as there are 3 separate storage/work rooms. Outside you can enjoy mountain views from the covered porch and the backyard has a large deck.  Minutes away from Fort Carson, Powers Corridor, and shopping.  Home is close to parks and walking trails. Additional items: complete water filtration/reverse osmosis system, detergent-less cold water laundry system, and radon mitigation system.
